<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Currently noController setting in viewRenderer reset for each controller.
I think noController setting should be global for all controller.</p>

<p>in my bootstrap:</p>

<p>$c=Zend_Controller_Front::getInstance();
$vr=Zend_Controller_Action_HelperBroker::getExistingHelper("viewRenderer");
$vr-&gt;setViewSuffix( "php"); // globally setting
$vr-&gt;setNoController( true );</p>

    </div>
